Textile is a text editing language that allows you to focus on content, which renders clean results in 100% valid XHTML. See below for usage.
<br /><br />
<table>
  <tr><th class="left">You write...</th><th class="left">...which produces</th></tr>
  <tr valign="top"><td class="code">_italic text_</td><td><i>italic text</i></td></tr>
  <tr valign="top"><td class="code">*bold text*</td><td><b>bold text</b></td></tr>
  <tr valign="top"><td class="code">h1. Heading 1</td><td><h1 style="color:#fff;">Heading 1</h1></td></tr>
  <tr valign="top"><td class="code">h2. Heading 2</td><td><h2 style="background-image:none;">Heading 2</h2></td></tr>
  <tr valign="top"><td class="code">* Item 1<br />* Item 2</td><td><ul><li>Item 1</li><li>Item 2</li></ul></td></tr>
  <tr valign="top"><td class="code"># Item 1<br /># Item 2</td><td><ol><li>Item 1</li><li>Item 2</li></ol></td></tr>
  <tr valign="top"><td class="code">"link":http://url.com</td><td><a href="http://url.com">link</a></td></tr>
</table>
